{"tid":202913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港，得「會計師」先成日劈炮唔撈去「尋理想」......","createTime":"2017-04-16T00:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T18:04:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"412b7078219d165d643664d07418ca78f5e3dd71","tid":202913,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T00:28:27.000Z","msg":"2016.04.16  Apple Daily<br />\n<br />\n............在梅窩經營麵包店有何困難？Kit說主要是人手不足，梅窩求職的居民不多，Kit只好日做夜做，朝7晚7，收舖再預備材料，每日工作15小時。<span style=\"color: red;\">當時男友現為丈夫的林俊傑（Sammy）.........，決定辭去收入可觀的審計師工作，搬到梅窩一齊打理麵包店</span>。父母對他的決定既失望又反對，Sammy回想說：「父母大約過了四年才開始接受我的決定，我知道他們仍然覺得好可惜。」"},{"pid":"c6bdf1be7dbd44b7c6f528a3a569e13035008d34","tid":202913,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2016.04.16  Apple Daily<br />\n<br />\n............在梅窩經營麵包店有何困難？Kit說主要是人手不足，梅窩求職的居民不多，Kit只好日做夜做，朝7晚7，收舖再預備材料，每日工作15小時。<span style=\"color: red;\">當時男友現為丈夫的林俊傑（Sammy）.........，決定辭去收入可觀的審計師工作，搬到梅窩一齊打理麵包店</span>。父母對他的決定既失望又反對，Sammy回想說：「父母大約過了四年才開始接受我的決定，我知道他們仍然覺得好可惜。」</blockquote><br />\n鬼咩，唔通同人講頂唔順？緊係老吹係尋理想"},{"pid":"c41ee8f1a95bda752865b6fdeb67fd8a7f1208f0","tid":202913,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"832888770a3137b4925225cc62a894d808407e76","tid":202913,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"之前有個拿1300萬退休金係銅鑼灣開餐廳<br />\n<br />\n夠勇!"},{"pid":"66cd3ebeb6c166cd856ea6b795c4bc4a204d52b8","tid":202913,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"反而同樣做到隻狗咁既工程同it狗好少轉行"},{"pid":"3d2e24d7bbbe65714d44a5d7c6873f0d2af00039","tid":202913,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而同樣做到隻狗咁既工程同it狗好少轉行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為香港傳媒都係憎人富貴厭人貧。<br />\n做核數師一定人工高（姑勿論係唔係做四大），<br />\n唔做核數=放棄高薪厚職。<br />\n唔做IT=WFC，有乜報道價值？<br />\n<br />\n台灣好耐之前有電子傳媒講個後生仔唔做IT走去做小食，個攤檔貼晒IT Cert，叫人唔好讀IT。"},{"pid":"28f88b4a818ef8d16e0bd23b901ffd07e3e6c6c2","tid":202913,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前有個拿1300萬退休金係銅鑼灣開餐廳<br />\n<br />\n夠勇!</blockquote><br />\n果個真係痴線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拎去買樓仲好"},{"pid":"030cf9701edf634d5f171a049d1eb6ed850dc601","tid":202913,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前有個拿1300萬退休金係銅鑼灣開餐廳<br />\n<br />\n夠勇!</blockquote><br />\n果個真係痴線<br />\n<br />\n拎去買樓仲好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炒樓應已變2000萬<br />\n<br />\n佢家陣1300萬裝修費應未回本, 仲要每月租金40萬, 未計人工食材"},{"pid":"ae1587fa88ea5a102f0b20e0b1eeb0ad573133d6","tid":202913,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:58:53.000Z","msg":"睇下d回覆下下講錢就知香港幾可悲"},{"pid":"9de15c3d9003e921163aff90f20ebffaf36050c0","tid":202913,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下d回覆下下講錢就知香港幾可悲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15094380fbbbcfe194a8548bf0374503cf8162f4","tid":202913,"uid":86865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇下d回覆下下講錢就知香港幾可悲</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n世界各地，無錢最可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad846b3cda190c72f810b31c990e6a97b598a61","tid":202913,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇下d回覆下下講錢就知香港幾可悲</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n世界各地，無錢最可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><